    <item>
      <title>Permira 任命新领导层，开启私募股权投资公司新篇章</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-12/permira-names-new-top-leadership-in-next-chapter-for-pe-firm</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Permira 任命了两位新的联席管理合伙人，为该管理着约 800 亿欧元（860 亿美元）私募股权和信贷基金的投资公司的高层注入新的领导力量。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-12/permira-names-new-top-leadership-in-next-chapter-for-pe-firm</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Jun 2024 12:19:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟将对中国进口电动汽车征收最高 48% 的关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-12/eu-to-impose-additional-tariffs-on-ev-imports-from-china</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟将从下个月开始对从中国出口的电动汽车征收额外关税，税率最高可达 48%，此举将进一步加剧贸易紧张局势，并增加购买电动汽车的成本。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-12/eu-to-impose-additional-tariffs-on-ev-imports-from-china</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Jun 2024 09:47:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国限制乌拉圭首批亿万富翁拥有的金融科技企业</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-12/uk-restricts-fintech-owned-by-uruguay-s-first-ever-billionaires</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国监管机构对乌拉圭首批亿万富翁拥有的一家金融科技公司实施了一系列限制，这是英国监管机构对每天处理数亿美元交易的支付公司进行严厉打击的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-12/uk-restricts-fintech-owned-by-uruguay-s-first-ever-billionaires</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Jun 2024 08:50:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Uniper 与 Gazprom 断绝关系后欧洲天然气价格上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-12/european-gas-rises-after-uniper-breaks-ties-with-gazprom</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在德国 Uniper SE 因未供应天然气而从俄罗斯天然气工业股份公司 (Gazprom PJSC) 获得超过 130 亿欧元（140 亿美元）的赔偿后，欧洲天然气价格大幅上涨，这增加了俄罗斯剩余燃料供应的不确定性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-12/european-gas-rises-after-uniper-breaks-ties-with-gazprom</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Jun 2024 08:08:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲加快振兴资产支持债券市场的计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-12/europe-speeds-up-plan-to-revive-asset-backed-securities-market</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲正在加大努力，降低银行筹集资金的成本，并将风险转移到资本市场，以便释放数十亿美元用于国防和绿色转型。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-12/europe-speeds-up-plan-to-revive-asset-backed-securities-market</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Jun 2024 05:00:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国工业数据和通胀降温迹象推动油价上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-june-12</link>
      <description><![CDATA[行业数据显示美国原油库存减少，而全球最大经济体的通胀数据低于预期，推动油价延续涨势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-june-12</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 23:25:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>债券交易员重仓押注美联储降息，股市上涨：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于通胀降温的迹象增强了人们对美联储今年将降息的预期，股票期货上涨，债券收益率下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
